{"tid":525741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千人等接駁巴 多人打尖引發混亂　　　","createTime":"2018-01-11T03:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-11T03:35:51.000Z","uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"06b26163640f5f1d2c20969d6270603f27593dc8","tid":525741,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T03:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180111/large/1515641057_43bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180111%2Flarge%2F1515641057_43bd.jpg&h=00684389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180111/large/1515640987_cc7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180111%2Flarge%2F1515640987_cc7a.jpg&h=f73cf19e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上9時15分許，港鐵東鐵綫疑發生訊號故障，全線服務暫停，港鐵已安排免費接駁巴士，接載受影響乘客。接駁巴士沿途只停大圍站，沙田站，火炭站，大學站，大埔墟站，太和站，粉嶺站及上水站，不停羅湖站。<br />\n<br />\n在九龍塘站外，估計高峰時有近千名受影響乘客湧出車站外，等候接駁巴士服務，現場雖然有架起鐵欄維持秩序，但由於人數太多，當有接駁巴士扺達時，部份不守秩序的市民，從人龍中攀過鐵欄插隊打尖，再衝上接駁巴士，引起排頭位乘客不滿，情況一度混亂。目前有警員在場維持秩序，輪候人數剩下約100人，大致平靜。"}]}